description: Nothing brings people together like food, and no food does that better than tapas! One of Los Angeles' newest trucks, Tapa That is a truck for friendship, food, and community. Having put their 14 years of culinary experience to the task of creating this gourmet menu means that these ladies are going to bring you nothing but the most amazing tastes under the SoCal sun. Two friends, a dream, and an all new food truck - what could be better than that?
name: Tapa That
